Acked-by: Lee, Chun-Yi <jlee@suse.com>
---
 arch/x86/boot/compressed/head_32.S      |   17 ++++++++++++
 arch/x86/boot/compressed/head_64.S      |   42 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++---
